original_title: Jethro Tull - Live at The Hippodrome
overview: Near perfect quality proshot footage of Jethro Tull, From the Hippodrome, in London England, on February 10th, 1977.  Total running time is 57 minutes, quality is about 9/10, and features the following tracks:  Skating away on the thin ice of a new day  Jack in the green  Thick as a brick  Songs from the wood  Velvet green  Hunting girl  Aqualung  Guitar solo  Wind up  Locomotive breath
title: Jethro Tull - Live at The Hippodrome
